commit.message: Added link to our devpost from main page
Added html template instead of manually generating html from python. Returns audio files using send_file instead of generating response.
Configured gunicorn to launch 2 workers per instance.
quickly added check for invalid files; also removed useless git entries
Fully functional on app engine. Stores and retrieves audio files from cloud storage. voiceOutput returns audio data rather than saving it to disk.
No longer requires saving of uploaded image. image_ocr now takes image file instead of path.
Fix to get app running on app engine
Changed directory structure and added files for Google Cloud App Engine.
Specified language in document for classify_text to avoid errors

Merge pull request #1 from sallyjyl/fix

Fixed caching issue by appending timestamp to mp3 file names
